Mapped /Users/dev/monorepo/services/auth/src/oauth/CLAUDE.md -> feature: "OAuth Integration" (project: "Auth Service")
```

**Map a task directory:**
```
$ brain map ./services/auth/src/oauth/pkce task:i9j0k1l2
Mapped /Users/dev/monorepo/services/auth/src/oauth/pkce/CLAUDE.md -> task: "Implement PKCE flow" (project: "Auth Service")
```

**Re-map (idempotent):**
```
$ brain map ./services/auth project:a1b2c3d4
Mapped /Users/dev/monorepo/services/auth/CLAUDE.md -> project: "Auth Service" (project: "Auth Service")
```
(Updates existing markers in place.)

**Unmap:**
